title: Verify "www.example.com/examplepath" matched the url list of "www.EXAMPLE.com/EXAMPLEPATH"
custom_summary: Verify "www.example.com/examplepath" matched the url list of "www.EXAMPLE.com/EXAMPLEPATH"
custom_preconds:
1. case-insensitive-url is enabled
2. Custom URL list configured with domains containing mixed case characters.
custom_steps:
1. Configure a custom URL list with domains containing mixed case characters.
2. Send url lookup requests with URLs containing domains with a different mix of upper and lower case characters.
custom_expected: NSProxy should correctly handle URLs with mixed case domain parts according to the configured case sensitivity setting for domain matching.
